title: New ‘Latinas in Academia Lecture Series’ focuses on grad school (California State University, Fresno)
text: ( Source : California State University, Fresno ) The new ' Latinas in Academia Lecture Series ' designed to encourage undergraduates to consider graduate school will run from noon - 1 p.m. Monday, Oct. 19 in the University Student Union , room
